  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.4">
<l>nañcu cōrvatōr veñciṉa varavam veruvi vantuniṉ caraṇeṉac caraṇāy</l>
<l>neñciṟ koṇṭuniṉ ṉañciṟaip paṟavaik kaṭaikka lamkoṭut taruḷceyta taṟintu</l>
<l>veñco lāḷarkaḷ namaṉṟamar kaṭiyar koṭiya ceyvaṉa vuḷavataṟ kaṭiyēṉ</l>
<l>añci vantuniṉ ṉaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkattam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a vicious, angry serpent, dripping poison,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming [to you] being fearful, said, “[Give me] your protection,”</l>
<l>You gave him sanctuary from your lovely wide-winged bird,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming [his] protection, taking [him] into your heart,</l>
<l>Granting [him] grace; knowing of this, [and] since the violent actions</l>
<l rend="indent">of Yama’s harsh-worded, cruel agents are real,</l>
<l>Coming [to you] fearing that, I, your servant, took refuge at your two feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">	lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
